{"tid":1155864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"竹園南邨女子墮樓亡 留言對不起丈夫女兒","createTime":"2019-05-15T08:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T10:21:20.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c678ac9c7d5220fc270a41f2e1a627e264548f78","tid":1155864,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UfPwZoe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfPwZoe.png&h=7b18f7e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FiLL3PV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFiLL3PV.png&h=93da2362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死者留字條稱對不起丈夫和女兒。張培生攝<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙竹園南邨華園樓，下午2時半左右，一名女子由高處墮下，當場不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查顯示，死者姓吳58歲，現場遺下死者的銀包，內有證件及一張紙，寫上「對不起，老公，我先行一步。女：對唔住Sorry」，現正了解其尋死原因。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=79716429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"9ecbab6aae02d2deaeb8382a24c60bb48b16c22b","tid":1155864,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:43:16.000Z","msg":"寫左等於無寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f0845473869d7faf6082df310f3d2827ac165d","tid":1155864,"uid":44243,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:45:25.000Z","msg":"有勇氣道歉無勇氣生存"},{"pid":"b664e821aa36d5bbec27849d78c62f6f262724da","tid":1155864,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9f0845473869d7faf6082df310f3d2827ac165d","tid":1155864,"uid":44243,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:45:25.0